{"tid":232771,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"又係XX 76歲老師猥褻12名男女小學生","createTime":"2017-05-07T04:40:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-07T04:42:59.000Z","uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b0cc9ee63ec073414660025dfa2d77d619b726a5","tid":232771,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T04:40:26.000Z","msg":"中部山區偏遠國小驚傳學生遭老師集體猥褻案！當地一名76歲劉姓耆老精通10多族的原住民語，去年6月起受聘到國小授課，卻利用師權在課堂上撥放A片，甚至對男、女學童撫胸、摸私處進行猥褻，3月底劉男噁劣行徑曝光，教育局、社會局與警方介入調查，掌握至少12名學童受害，警方前天將劉男拘提到案，依強制猥褻罪移送後裁定收押。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/hot/20170507/1113334\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fhot%2F20170507%2F1113334&d=P3odlOe4J5oN5vIqyIzMU3Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=4ab594a9\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/hot/20170507/1113334</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170507/640_e743079e2aec1589537a1860aca0cfad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170507%2F640_e743079e2aec1589537a1860aca0cfad.jpg&h=b7d90ede&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />台灣"},{"pid":"335a1cf9c919f91e8beac085ab31d2e477169350","tid":232771,"uid":89182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T04:42:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}